On September 1 97, PMI simultaneously launched Marlboro Menthol KS Box (16mg tar and Menthol Lights KS Box (9mg tar) in Colombia. These two products became KOOL's direct competitors (Premium Menthol Brands).
At the same time KOOL replaced its product with a milder 11mg cigarette (the same KOOL Milds but with a 27mm cork tipping).
